  triage:title "RBP-004: raw String fields for boundary_id/sprint in inventory.rs - format invariants checked ad hoc" ;
  triage:description "crates/sc-lint-boundary/src/inventory.rs:43 uses raw String fields for boundary_id, sprint, and similar identifiers where format invariants (e.g. valid boundary id format, non-empty sprint name) are checked ad hoc throughout the codebase rather than enforced at construction via newtypes. RBP-004 requires format-constrained identifiers to use validated newtypes." ;
